        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Confirmed them - Strengthened them; that is, by their instructions and exhortations. See the notes on Acts 14:22. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "Confirmed them - Strengthened them; that is, by their instructions and exhortations. See the notes on ",
